title: BBC WS - George Wheeler's 'To Make The People Smile Again
description:
BBC WS - George Wheeler's 'To Make The People Smile Again'
Adapted by Steve Chambers
Directed by Marion Nancarrow
Broadcast January 6, 2007
Coded from tape at 128/44.1

Londoner George Wheeler's experiences with
The International Brigades in Spain during
the Spanish Civil War.

Cast includes
George Wheeler - Ben Crow
Andre - William Hope
Silvano - Daniel Delasandro
Kevin - Andrew Robb
John Danlow - Mark Bonner
Gus - John Schwab
Jim - Brian Mclasky
Proctor - Simon Trinder
